@startuml
!theme plain

title Diagramme de sequence - Creation ordonnance

autonumber

actor Medecin
boundary Frontend as "Application Angular"
control API as "Backend Spring Boot"
control ServiceOrdonnance as "Service Ordonnance"
database DB as "Base de donnees"

Medecin -> Frontend: Saisir ordonnance
Frontend -> API: POST /ordonnances (details)
API -> ServiceOrdonnance: verifierPatientEtMedicaments(details)
ServiceOrdonnance -> DB: Lire patient + medicaments
DB --> ServiceOrdonnance: Donnees de reference

alt Donnees valides
  ServiceOrdonnance -> DB: Inserer ordonnance + lignes
  DB --> ServiceOrdonnance: idOrdonnance
  ServiceOrdonnance --> API: Ordonnance enregistree
  API --> Frontend: 201 Created + idOrdonnance
  Frontend --> Medecin: Afficher ordonnance
else Donnees invalides
  ServiceOrdonnance --> API: Erreur metier
  API --> Frontend: 422 Unprocessable Entity
  Frontend --> Medecin: Corriger les champs
end

@enduml
